Template: raspberrypi-sys-mods/allow_3p_repos
Type: select
Choices: yes, no, purge
Default: no
_Description: Allow adding third party repositories?
 This package may add third party repositories and keys when upgrading. Please
 choose whether or not you want these repositories to be added.
 .
  - yes: new third party repositories may be added;
  - no: new third party repositories will not be added;
  - purge: new third party repositories will not be added, and previously add third party repositories will be purged;
